
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Application Cancel</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Poppins' , sans-serif; font-size:14px;color:#302c2b; line-height:2;">
    <div class="rt-tb-scrl">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>
            @if (Model.Apptype == "OSG")
            {
                if (Model.vendorMail_f == true)
                {
                    <p>Kindly cancel the recently released @Model.Cancel_f of <b>@Model.PersonName</b> for the post of  <b>@Model.DesignationName</b>(@Model.TypeofAppointment) with effect from <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> and inform the same to the candidate.</p>
                }
                else if (Model.Cancel_f == "Office Order" || Model.Cancel_f == "Extension Order" || Model.Cancel_f == "Enhancement Order")
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to your cancellation request, the appointment letter of <b>@Model.PersonName </b> for the post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> (@Model.TypeofAppointment) under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b>. with effect from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> will be treated as <b>Cancelled</b>.</p>
                }
                else if (Model.Cancel_f == "Verification level")
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to your cancellation request, the offer letter of <b>@Model.PersonName </b> for the post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> (@Model.TypeofAppointment) under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b>. with effect from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> will be treated as <b>Cancelled</b>.</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to your cancellation request, the application of <b>@Model.PersonName </b> for the post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> (@Model.TypeofAppointment) under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b>. with effect from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> will be treated as <b>Cancelled</b>.</p>
                }
                <p>For any queries, please mail to <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment5@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment5@imail.iitm.ac.in</a> / <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in</a> and we will get back to you at the earliest.</p>
            }
            else
            {
                if (Model.Cancel_f == "Office Order" || Model.Cancel_f == "Extension Order" || Model.Cancel_f == "Enhancement Order")
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to your request, the @Model.Cancel_f dated : <b>@Model.OfficeOrderDate</b> issued to <b>@Model.PersonName , @Model.DesignationName</b> under the project no <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> has been cancelled.</p>
                    <p>Note: The Commitment amount booked for the staff will be withdrawn and credited to the project.</p>
                }
                else if (Model.Cancel_f == "Verification level")
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to the request received for offer <b>cancellation</b>.</p>
                    <p>The offer letter issued to <b>@Model.PersonName , @Model.DesignationName</b> in the <b>@Model.Department</b> under the project no <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b>, will be treated as cancelled.</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to your cancellation request, the application of <b>@Model.PersonName </b> for the post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> (@Model.TypeofAppointment) under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b>. with effect from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> will be treated as <b>Cancelled</b>.</p>
                }
                <p>For any queries, kindly send an email to <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment2@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment2@imail.iitm.ac.in </a>/<a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in</a> and we will get back to you at the earliest.</p>

            }

            <p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px;">
                @Model.DAName<br>
                Project Recruitment<br>
                Centre for IC&SR<br>
                IIT Madras<br>
                *This is a system generated email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
